    "Figure 1 illustrates its principal usage for document and molecule retrieval.",
    "A molecule can be searched with asdrawn, similarity, or substructure search, and a list of patents referencing the molecule is retrieved.",
    "On the other hand, molecules selected from a specific document can be extracted and then leveraged to browse and explore the document.",
